Package com.opengamma.strata.market.value Description

Package containing values of market data.

Each type in this package stores or defines a kind of market data. The generic term "value" is used for the package, however individual types prefer to use more specific names, such as "discount factors" or "Ibor rates".

Each type of value is associated with a key, found in the com.opengamma.strata.market.key package.
